msgid "环境模块"
msgstr "Environment Modules"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:4
msgid "本部分介绍如何创建和使用环境模块。"
msgstr "This section covers how to create and work with environment modules."

#: ../../env_modules.rst:7
msgid "创建自定义模块"
msgstr "Creating Custom Modules"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:10
msgid "继承 EnvBase"
msgstr "Inherit from EnvBase"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:12
msgid "要创建自定义环境模块，请继承 ``EnvBase`` 并实现必需的方法："
msgstr ""
"To create a custom environment module, inherit from ``EnvBase`` and "
"implement the required methods:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:15
msgid "需要实现的方法"
msgstr "Required Methods to Implement"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:17
msgid "创建自定义环境模块时，必须实现："
msgstr "When creating a custom environment module, you must implement:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:19
msgid "**async def step(self, tick: int, t: datetime) -> None**"
msgstr "**async def step(self, tick: int, t: datetime) -> None**"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:21
msgid "执行一个模拟步骤。在 AgentSociety 模拟期间自动调用。 使用此方法更新时间相关的状态。"
msgstr ""
"Execute one simulation step. This is called automatically during "
"AgentSociety simulations. Use this to update time-dependent state."

#: ../../env_modules.rst:24
msgid "参数:"
msgstr "Parameters:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:25
msgid "tick: 此步骤的持续时间（秒） t: 此步骤后的当前模拟日期时间"
msgstr ""
"tick: Duration of this step in seconds t: Current simulation datetime after "
"this step"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:28
msgid "**使用 @tool 装饰的工具**"
msgstr "**Tools decorated with @tool**"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:30
msgid "使用 ``@tool`` 装饰器将方法公开为智能体的可调用函数。"
msgstr ""
"Use the ``@tool`` decorator to expose methods as callable functions for "
"agents."

#: ../../env_modules.rst:53
msgid "参考实现"
msgstr "Reference Implementation"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:55
msgid "有关完整的参考实现，请参阅："
msgstr "For complete reference implementations, see:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:57
msgid "``SimpleSocialSpace`` - 社交互动模块"
msgstr "``SimpleSocialSpace`` - Social interaction module"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:58
msgid "``PublicGoodsEnv`` - 公共物品博弈模块"
msgstr "``PublicGoodsEnv`` - Public goods game module"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:59
msgid "``PrisonersDilemmaEnv`` - 囚徒困境模块"
msgstr "``PrisonersDilemmaEnv`` - Prisoner's dilemma module"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:62
msgid "@tool 装饰器"
msgstr "The @tool Decorator"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:64
msgid "``@tool`` 装饰器将方法标记为可被智能体调用："
msgstr "The ``@tool`` decorator marks methods as callable by agents:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:75
msgid "参数："
msgstr "Parameters:"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:77
msgid ""
"**readonly** (bool): 工具是否修改环境 * ``True`` = 只读，可用于查询 * ``False`` = 修改状态，可用于干预"
msgstr ""
"**readonly** (bool): Whether the tool modifies the environment * ``True`` = "
"read-only, can be used in queries * ``False`` = modifies state, can be used "
"in interventions"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:81
msgid ""
"**kind** (str): 工具的类型 * ``\"observe\"``: 单参数观察（需要 readonly=True） * "
"``\"statistics\"``: 聚合查询（无参数，需要 readonly=True） * ``None`` 或省略: 常规工具（任何签名，任何 "
"readonly 值）"
msgstr ""
"**kind** (str): The type of tool * ``\"observe\"``: Single-parameter "
"observations (requires readonly=True) * ``\"statistics\"``: Aggregate "
"queries (no parameters, requires readonly=True) * ``None`` or omitted: "
"Regular tool (any signature, any readonly value)"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:87
msgid "工具类型"
msgstr "Tool Types"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:89
msgid "**observe**: 单参数观察（需要 readonly=True）"
msgstr "**observe**: Single-parameter observations (readonly=True required)"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:90
msgid "**statistics**: 聚合查询（无参数，需要 readonly=True）"
msgstr ""
"**statistics**: Aggregate queries (no parameters, readonly=True required)"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:91
msgid "**regular**: 任何其他工具（可以是只读或读写）"
msgstr "**regular**: Any other tool (can be readonly or read-write)"

#: ../../env_modules.rst:93
msgid "有关工具类型的更多详情，请参阅 :doc:`concepts`。"
msgstr "See :doc:`concepts` for more details on tool types."

